    <h1>Your <em>keeper stones</em>, and the library that holds them</h1>
    <p class="lede">Long before crystal healing became a phrase in a shop window, the human animal reached for the mineral world to steady itself. A stone is a fixed point you can carry, a piece of deep-time patience small enough to pocket. Enter your date of birth and the Oracle names the stones the tradition assigns to you, then read the full cabinet below.</p>
